k(1x), privily(1x), secret(1x)"},"H6846":{"id":"H6846","lemma":"צְפַנְיָה","translit":"Tsᵉphanyâh","pron":"tsef-an-yaw'","derivation":"or צְפַנְיָהוּ; from H6845 (צָפַן) and H3050 (יָהּ); Jah has secreted;","strongs_def":"Tsephanjah, the name of four Israelites","kjv_def":"Zephaniah.","pos":"proper masculine noun","usage":"Zephaniah(10x)"},"H6847":{"id":"H6847","lemma":"צׇפְנַת פַּעְנֵחַ","translit":"Tsophnath Paʻnêach","pron":"tsof-nath' pah-nay'-akh","derivation":"of Egyptian derivation;","strongs_def":"Tsophnath-Paneach, Joseph's Egyptian name","kjv_def":"Zaphnath-paaneah.","pos":"proper masculine noun","usage":"Zaphnathpaaneah(1x)"},"H6848":{"id":"H6848","lemma":"צֶפַע","translit":"tsephaʻ","pron":"tseh'-fah or tsiphoniy tsif-o-nee'","derivation":"from an unused root meaning to extrude;","strongs_def":"a viper (as thrusting out the tongue, i.e. hissing)","kjv_def":"adder, cockatrice.","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"cockatrice(4x), adder(1x)"},"H6849":{"id":"H6849","lemma":"צְפִעָה","translit":"tsᵉphiʻâh","pron":"tsef-ee-aw'","derivation":"feminine from the same as H6848 (צֶפַע);","strongs_def":"an outcast thing","kjv_def":"issue.","pos":"feminine noun","usage":"issue(1x)"},"H6850":{"id":"H6850","lemma":"צָפַף","translit":"tsâphaph","pron":"tsaw-faf'","derivation":"a primitive root;","strongs_def":"to coo or chirp (as a bird)","kjv_def":"chatter, peep, whisper.","pos":"verb","usage":"peep(2x), chatter(1x), whisper(1x)"},"H6851":{"id":"H6851","lemma":"צַפְצָפָה","translit":"tsaphtsâphâh","pron":"tsaf-tsaw-faw'","derivation":"from H6687 (צוּף);","strongs_def":"a willow (as growing in overflowed places)","kjv_def":"willow tree."},"H6852":{"id":"H6852","lemma":"צָפַר","translit":"tsâphar","pron":"tsaw-far'","derivation":"a primitive root;","strongs_def":"to skip about, i.e. return","kjv_def":"depart early.","pos":"verb"},"H6853":{"id":"H6853","lemma":"צְפַר","translit":"tsᵉphar","pron":"tsef-ar'","derivation":"(Aramaic) corresponding to H6833 (צִפּוֹר);","strongs_de