oot meaning to pierce; puncture;","strongs_def":"Tseredah, a place in Palestine","kjv_def":"Zereda, Zeredathah."},"H6869":{"id":"H6869","lemma":"צָרָה","translit":"tsârâh","pron":"tsaw-raw'","derivation":"feminine of H6862 (צַר);","strongs_def":"tightness (i.e. figuratively, trouble); transitively, a female rival:","kjv_def":"adversary, adversity, affliction, anguish, distress, tribulation, trouble.","pos":"feminine noun","usage":"trouble(44x), distress(8x), affliction(7x), adversity(5x), anguish(5x), tribulation(3x), adversary(1x)"},"H6870":{"id":"H6870","lemma":"צְרוּיָה","translit":"Tsᵉrûwyâh","pron":"tser-oo-yaw'","derivation":"feminine passive participle from the same as H6875 (צְרִי); wounded;","strongs_def":"Tserujah, an Israelitess","kjv_def":"Zeruiah."},"H6871":{"id":"H6871","lemma":"צְרוּעָה","translit":"Tsᵉrûwʻâh","pron":"tser-oo-aw'","derivation":"feminine passive participle of H6879 (צָרַע); leprous;","strongs_def":"Tseruah, an Israelitess","kjv_def":"Zeruah."},"H6872":{"id":"H6872","lemma":"צְרוֹר","translit":"tsᵉrôwr","pron":"tser-ore'","derivation":"or (shorter) צְרֹר; from H6887 (צָרַר);","strongs_def":"a parcel (as packed up); also a kernel or particle (as if a package)","kjv_def":"bag, [idiom] bendeth, bundle, least grain, small stone.","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"bundle(4x), bag(3x), bindeth(1x), grain(1x), stone(1x), Zeror(1x)"},"H6873":{"id":"H6873","lemma":"צָרַח","translit":"tsârach","pron":"tsaw-rakh'","derivation":"a primitive root;","strongs_def":"to be clear (in tone, i.e. shrill), i.e. to whoop","kjv_def":"cry, roar.","pos":"verb","usage":"cry(1x), roar(1x)"},"H6874":{"id":"H6874","lemma":"צְרִי","translit":"Tsᵉrîy","pron":"tser-ee'","derivation":"the same as H6875 (צְרִי);","strongs_def":"Tseri, an Israelite","kjv_def":"Zeri. Compare H3340 (יִצְרִי)."},"H6875":{"id":"H6875","lemma":"צְרִי","translit":"tsᵉrîy","pron":"tser-ee'","derivation":"or צֳרִי; from an unused root meaning to crack (as by pressure), hence, to leak;","strongs_de